## AgentConfig-D2 Profession Registry (v2)
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `crates/auto-forge/src/relay/profession.rs`
**Tags:** stack:backend
**Depends on:** AgentConfig-G1, Specs-G1

```rust
pub struct Profession {
    pub id: String,
    pub name: String,
    pub phase: ForgePhase,
    pub owned_sections: Vec<SectionType>,
    pub readable_sections: Vec<SectionType>,
    pub allowed_tools: Vec<String>,
    pub handoff_to: Vec<String>,
    pub approval_gates: Vec<String>,
    pub max_turns: u32,
    pub token_budget: u64,
}
```


| Profession | Phase | Owned Specs | Model Tier | Gate |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Assistant | Intake | None | Light | Auto |
| Advisor | Discovery | Goals | Medium | Human (GSD) / Human (Check) |
| Architect | Design | Architecture, Designs | Heavy | Auto (GSD) / Human (Check) |
| Planner | Planning | Plans | Medium | Auto |
| Coder | Execution | None (code) | Heavy | Auto |
| Tester | Execution | Tests | Medium | Auto |
| Reviewer | Verification | Reviews | Heavy | Auto |
| Documenter | Report | Reports | Light | Auto |

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | `String` | profession identifier |
| `phase` | `ForgePhase` | which phase this profession runs in |
| `owned_sections` | `Vec<SectionType>` | specs this profession can write |
| `readable_sections` | `Vec<SectionType>` | specs this profession can read |
| `approval_gates` | `Vec<String>` | handoff targets that require approval |


